{"image_id": "MPC_2015_page_58", "image_size": [1257, 1632], "ocr": [{"text": "Asphalt. We have refinery-based asphalt production capacity of up to 101 mbpcd, which includes asphalt", "bbox": [153.2, 149.6, 1103.6, 170.6]}, {"text": "cements, polymer-modified asphalt, emulsified asphalt, industrial asphalts and roofing flux. We have a broad", "bbox": [153.2, 174.8, 1103.7, 195.7]}, {"text": "customer base, including asphalt-paving contractors, government entities (states, counties, cities and townships)", "bbox": [153.2, 199.8, 1103.7, 220.7]}, {"text": "and asphalt roofing shingle manufacturers. We sell asphalt in the domestic and export wholesale markets via rail,", "bbox": [153.2, 224.8, 1103.6, 245.7]}, {"text": "barge and vessel.", "bbox": [153.2, 249.8, 296.3, 270.7]}, {"text": "Terminals", "bbox": [153.2, 304.0, 241.2, 324.9]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2015, we owned and operated 61 light product and 18 asphalt terminals. Our light product", "bbox": [153.2, 339.0, 1103.7, 359.9]}, {"text": "and asphalt terminals averaged 1,410 mbpd and 32 mbpd of throughput in 2015, respectively. In addition, we", "bbox": [153.2, 364.1, 1103.8, 384.9]}, {"text": "distribute refined products through one leased light product terminal, two light product terminals in which we", "bbox": [153.2, 389.1, 1103.8, 409.9]}, {"text": "have partial ownership interests but do not operate and approximately 120 third-party light product and two third-", "bbox": [153.2, 414.1, 1103.6, 434.9]}, {"text": "party asphalt terminals in our market area. The following table sets forth additional details about our owned and", "bbox": [153.2, 439.1, 1103.8, 459.9]}, {"text": "operated terminals at December 31, 2015.", "bbox": [153.2, 464.1, 502.9, 484.9]}, {"text": "Owned and Operated Terminals", "bbox": [153.2, 541.6, 393.5, 560.3]}, {"text": "Number of", "bbox": [633.9, 522.8, 715.7, 541.6]}, {"text": "Terminals", "bbox": [636.8, 541.6, 712.9, 560.3]}, {"text": "Tank Storage", "bbox": [766.1, 504